title: Efficient Labor Regulations
description: In 2024, Morocco achieved an operational efficiency score of 32.17 in labor regulations and public services, indicating a streamlined and effective labor system.

title: Minimal Tariff Lines with Specific Rates for All Products
description: As of 2021, only 0.0008% of Morocco's tariff lines for all products had specific rates, reflecting a competitive trade environment.

title: Low Specific Tariff Rates on Primary Products
description: In 2021, Morocco maintained a low percentage of 0.0071% for tariff lines with specific rates on primary products, promoting trade flexibility.
